ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3772a2f9d6d04a2b2efb83400ee8e88a76e09d","tid":1461960,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"這類型的健身室的好處是不會狂sell你，我不想join Physical, 有什麼24/7的健身室好推介😀? My friend Jason who&rsquo;s a gym membership salesman is going to send a follow-up email and make a follow-up call to a customer who&rsquo;s interested in joining the ten year membership. I used to work at a gym and whenever a customer paid a visit to the gym I always followed it up with a call or an email. Some of my colleagues followed it up with a visit to the customer. My friend Ken who wants to join his gym had a meeting yesterday and a follow-up has been scheduled for tomorrow. He&rsquo;s also writing a follow-up to the acclaimed &ldquo;the invisible man&rdquo; so he&rsquo;s so busy that he won&rsquo;t have time to pay a follow-up visit to the gym for the time being. Therefore I handed Ken the membership agreement for Jason and will follow up with him in the next couple days. A few days ago he complained that he was treated badly at Starbucks. As a result, the barista provided a referral to a senior staff member who in turn referred his case to the manager. He&rsquo;ll follow up the case with the manager to be sure that it&rsquo;ll be dealt with seriously. In addition, he&rsquo;s been suffering from a stroke so I referred him to a cardiologist. Ken recently posted on an online forum to suggest building an art gallery to boost tourism which was supported by many people on the forum. They asked the forum administrator for a referral to the district councilor. They&rsquo;ll follow up with the district councilor on the matter being discussed. I too will follow up on the issue. His suggestion of building an art museum is deemed appropriate."},{"pid":"75876134e1e651452ed58211d33f00f8ab832e73","tid":1461960,"u